OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain clearing to the east
OL,6,Fthrough early morning to leave sunny
OL,7,Fspells with a few showers for the rest
OL,8,Fof the day. Strong winds around the
OL,9,Fcoast with winds strengthening inland
OL,10,Ffrom late morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear spells and a few
OL,13,Fshowers at first this evening. Soon
OL,14,Fturning cloudier with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain overnight, these may be heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes. Strong winds, especially near
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
