OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA largely cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fbrighter spells and showers, which may
OL,7,Fbe heavy at times. Strong
OL,8,Fsouthwesterly winds which may reach
OL,9,Fgale force before easing in the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers Monday. Dry start
OL,14,Fwith rain possible later on Tuesday.
OL,15,FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Fon Wednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,17,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
